6/4/22, 17:10 - Arun Bbs: Respected Sir
We have opted for Fastrack semester which will only be of two months duration. However, we have been asked to pay hostel and mess fees for the whole semester which generally spans for at least 4-5 months. This is very unfair and burdensome to the students. Some families are yet to recover from the financial crisis due to COVID-19. A number of colleges have taken supportive measures such as reducing tuition fees and hostel fees during this period. In contrast, we have been asked to pay hostel fees for a complete general semester when we wouldn't be staying in hostels for half the duration. I would kindly request you to consider our proposal and reduce hostel and mess fees as per the two month period.
